OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781695157
OL,3,CBorder Force makes its largest ever
OL,4,Ccannabis seizure of 12 tonnes worth
OL,5,C#139m
OL,7,FOfficers have seized 12 tonnes of
OL,8,Fcannabis worth around #139 million in
OL,9,Fthe Border Force's largest ever
OL,10,Fseizure of the drug.
OL,12,FSome 1,200 boxes of cannabis were
OL,13,Ffound crammed into two shipping
OL,14,Fcontainers at Southampton Port which
OL,15,Fhad arrived from Canada, the Home
OL,16,FOffice said.
OL,18,FHome Office intelligence analysts
OL,19,Fworked with Canadian officials and UK
OL,20,Flaw enforcement to identify the two
OL,21,Fcontainers on their way to Southampton.
