OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781695157
OL,3,CBorder Force makes its largest ever
OL,4,Ccannabis seizure of 12 tonnes worth
OL,5,C#139m
OL,7,FThe delivery was intercepted on May 6,
OL,8,Fthe Home Office said, and the drugs
OL,9,Fseized make up the largest ever Border
OL,10,FForce cannabis seizure, at four tonnes
OL,11,Fmore than the previous largest seizure
OL,12,Fin 2017.
OL,14,FMigration minister Mike Tapp said:
OL,15,F"Congratulations to our brilliant
OL,16,FBorder Force officers for this record-
OL,17,Fbreaking haul.
OL,19,F"We will not allow criminal gangs to
OL,20,Fprofit from misery and peddle their
OL,21,Fvile trade.
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@AOU
