OL,3,CBorder Force makes its largest ever
OL,4,Ccannabis seizure of 12 tonnes worth
OL,5,C#139m
OL,7,F"More than ever before, we are working
OL,8,Fwith policing and international
OL,9,Fpartners to secure our borders and
OL,10,Fkeep our streets safe."
OL,12,FThe Home Office said the South West
OL,13,FRegional Organised Crime Unit arrested
OL,14,Fthree people on suspicion of
OL,15,Ffacilitating importations on Tuesday.
